  <description type="morphology">Stems 0.5–2 dm. Basal leaves palmate to subpalmate; distal 1/2–2/3 of leaflet margins incised 3/4+ to midvein, undivided medial blade 1.5–3 mm wide, teeth linear to narrowly oblong.</description>
